### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@academyId = PIp0OwatTywTYtbwgccpkmo51HuXoqFq

###############################################
# ASISTENCIA - Registro y Historial
###############################################
# Prefix: /api/academies/:academyId/attendance
# Requiere: sesion activa + pertenecer a la academia
# Primero haz login en auth.http
###############################################

@groupId = d2156d8b-27b2-400a-ad24-367c0b428df9
@studentId = c89f49f9-8ea6-4416-a6c3-cefc2184c4ab

### ========================================
### REGISTRAR ASISTENCIA POR QR
### ========================================

### Registrar asistencia escaneando QR del alumno
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/attendance/qr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qr_data": "{\"affiliationNumber\":\"AF-001\",\"studentId\":\"c89f49f9-8ea6-4416-a6c3-cefc2184c4ab\",\"organizationId\":\"PIp0OwatTywTYtbwgccpkmo51HuXoqFq\"}",
  "group_id": "{{groupId}}"
}

### ========================================
### REGISTRAR ASISTENCIA POR NUMERO
### ========================================

### Registrar asistencia por numero de afiliacion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/attendance/number
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "affiliation_number": "AF-001",
  "group_id": "{{groupId}}"
}

### ========================================
### REGISTRAR ASISTENCIA MANUAL
### ========================================

### Registrar asistencia seleccionando alumno manualmente
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/attendance/manual
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "group_id": "{{groupId}}"
}

### ========================================
### HISTORIAL DE ASISTENCIA POR GRUPO
### ========================================

### Historial completo del grupo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/attendance/groups/{{groupId}}

### Historial del grupo en rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/attendance/groups/{{groupId}}?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-02-28

### Historial del grupo - solo febrero 2026
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/attendance/groups/{{groupId}}?from=2026-02-01&to=2026-02-28
